OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry morning with sunny
OL,6,Fspells. Staying largely dry in the
OL,7,Fafternoon and turning cloudier. Rain
OL,8,Fmay edge into western Argyll later.
OL,9,FLight winds becoming strong
OL,10,Fsoutheasterlies over western Argyll
OL,11,Flater with a risk of gales.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FCloudy with heavy rain
OL,14,Fspreading eastwards. Rain clears to
OL,15,Fthe east overnight with dry conditions
OL,16,Fby morning. Strong to gale force
OL,17,Fsoutheasterly winds easing inland
OL,18,Flater in the night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
