OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA largely dry day with
OL,6,Fbright spells. Outbreaks of rain from
OL,7,Flate afternoon through the evening.
OL,8,FStrong winds around the coast with
OL,9,Fwinds strengthening inland later.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FHeavy
OL,12,Foutbreaks of rain on Sunday. Sunny
OL,13,Fspells on Monday with scattered
OL,14,Fshowers. Dry with sunny spells
OL,15,FTuesday. Winds will be strong with
OL,16,Frisk of gales Sunday, then becoming
OL,17,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
